Net Revenues – Net revenues decreased $70 million (0.3%) to $25,868 million in 2019, and Organic Net Revenue
increased $1,067 million (4.1%) to $26,879 million. Emerging markets net revenues increased 0.2%, including an
unfavorable currency impact, and emerging markets Organic Net Revenue increased 7.7%. The underlying changes in
net revenues and Organic Net Revenue are detailed below:
