across all categories except chocolate. The July 16, 2019 acquisition of a majority interest in Perfect Snacks added net
revenues of $53 million and the June 7, 2018 acquisition of Tate’s Bake Shop added incremental net revenues of $35
million in 2019. Unfavorable currency impact was due to the strength of the U.S. dollar relative to the Canadian dollar.
